data.description: House remodeled in 1990 then Beautifully updated in 2016/17.  Driveway has room for 4/5 cars and parking allowed in streets.  Primary approx. 23x13 and ensuite has a wet room with marble tile.  Wood floors throughout entire living area and gorgeous porcelain in EIK kitchen.  Property is large, level and private. Room for extended family. Come see this you won't be disappointed. P.S. Elementary school a couple of blocks away.
